## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **WHO 30+ year drug donation paradigm** = Merck Mectizan 1987 (ivermectin onchocerciasis + LF) 2.5B+ doses + GSK albendazole LF + Pfizer Zithromax trachoma + Eisai DEC + Novartis MDT leprosy. 단일 pharma → endemic-country WHO partnership 모델. 임상 RCT 통상 환자-pay 와 distinct.
2. **ACT artemisinin K13 mutation resistance** = Cambodia/Myanmar/Vietnam Greater Mekong subregion 첫 detection → 2024 East Africa (Eritrea + Rwanda + Uganda) K13 mutation 보고. ACT 단일-약 의존 paradigm 균열. quantum-VQE 의 PfATP4 + Kelch13 propeller domain leverage.
3. **benznidazole 2017 first FDA Chagas — 100년 후** = Carlos Chagas 1909 disease 기술 → 2017 FDA approval. DNDi + Bayer accelerated approval. nifurtimox Lampit oral 2020 follow. 미국 1.7M Latin-American immigrant 환자 inventory.
4. **양자-VQE 의 protease leverage** = T. cruzi cruzipain (cysteine protease, papain-family C1) 가 핵심 virulence factor. parasite-specific S2 pocket selectivity (vs human cathepsin) 가 VQE active-site comparative scoring 직접 fit. hxq-ntd-cruzipain-001 의 initial novel candidate 정당화.
5. **R21/Matrix-M malaria vaccine 2023 WHO recommend** = RTS,S/AS01 2021 first → R21/Matrix-M 2023 second. Oxford-Serum Institute India 협업 + circumsporozoite hepatitis-B core fusion. 75%+ efficacy demonstrated. Phase ε WEAVE/VIROCAPSID scaffold.
6. **bedaquiline + pretomanid + linezolid (BPaL) 2019** = MDR/XDR-TB 6-month regimen. 18-24 month 기존 regimen 의 1/3. linezolid neuropathy + clofazimine 추가 BPaLC research. WHO 2030 TB elimination 목표 핵심.
7. **fexinidazole 2018 first oral HAT** = DNDi 주도, melarsoprol arsenical injection (5% mortality) 종료. acoziborole single-dose oral late-stage trial. HAT global elimination 2030 plausible.
8. **tafenoquine + G6PD test 의무** = first single-dose radical cure P. vivax. 8-aminoquinoline class — primaquine 14-day vs tafenoquine single-dose. quantitative G6PD test (qualitative ≠ sufficient) 필수 — pharmacogenomics axis cross-link.
9. **global-health drug pricing model + 한국-tropical-disease 한정 임상 의의** = 한국 tropical NTD non-endemic. travel-medicine + immigrant-health + reverse-zoonosis (e.g., scrub typhus + Korean hemorrhagic fever Hantaan — separate) 한정. 본 entry 의 임상 의의 = global-health solidarity + WHO 2030 roadmap 기여 + Korean pharma generic 잠재 (DNDi 협업).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, NTD endemic-country 임상 의미 한정. WHO 2030 elimination roadmap 의 6+ NTD eliminate-as-public-health-problem 목표 (LF + onchocerciasis + trachoma + HAT gambiense + leprosy + Chagas vertical) tracking 만 가능.

